snippet.title: Jason T Smith
snippet.description:
www.JasonThrifts.com -  Meet America’s #1 Thrifter, Jason is an entertaining, fast paced, modern day treasure hunter. He will show you the in’s, out’s and adventures of thrifting for profit.

��With a sixth-sense for discovering deals, and the world of online auctions, Jason helps people turn second-hand goods into first-rate profit.  From taking the best photos, to write listing descriptions that sell all the way to how to pack it, label it and ship it to save you money.�

There ain’t no thrifter that thrifts like Jason Thrifts!
